  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The warrior who comes to the maze forest, all you have to do is destroy all the enemies and obstacles you can see! Regardless of mission or task, forget about it all! Just <strong>shoot! SHOOT! SHOOT & SHOOT!</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated destructible terrain (Yes, you can blow up <strong>EVERYTHING</strong>)!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn screen-shaking explosions into offensive weapons, shatter all enemies and obstacles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/4102ed6170c80e92cab80c0dd3a33c12.poster.avif?t=1743498014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/4102ed6170c80e92cab80c0dd3a33c12.webm?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/4102ed6170c80e92cab80c0dd3a33c12.mp4?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple shooting and aiming for beginners, no need to be an experienced shooter!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bullet Heaven</strong> (Not Hell!), dodge through enemy bullets with hero upgrades!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Incredible player build! Barrage shooting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/7f0f55288f13f10363bf22985a5d1756.poster.avif?t=1743498014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/7f0f55288f13f10363bf22985a5d1756.webm?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/7f0f55288f13f10363bf22985a5d1756.mp4?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 unhinged heroes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 reality-bending weapons (Meet your new friend: <i>The Forest Bomber</i>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150+ uncensored item combos (Stack 8 fire speed buffs? Go nuts!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ unique level templates!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-minute fast-paced runs (Perfect for lunch break carnage)!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The warrior who comes to the maze forest, all you have to do is destroy all the enemies and obstacles you can see! Regardless of mission or task, forget about it all! Just <strong>shoot! SHOOT! SHOOT & SHOOT!</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated destructible terrain (Yes, you can blow up <strong>EVERYTHING</strong>)!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn screen-shaking explosions into offensive weapons, shatter all enemies and obstacles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/4102ed6170c80e92cab80c0dd3a33c12.poster.avif?t=1743498014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/4102ed6170c80e92cab80c0dd3a33c12.webm?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/4102ed6170c80e92cab80c0dd3a33c12.mp4?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple shooting and aiming for beginners, no need to be an experienced shooter!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bullet Heaven</strong> (Not Hell!), dodge through enemy bullets with hero upgrades!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Incredible player build! Barrage shooting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/7f0f55288f13f10363bf22985a5d1756.poster.avif?t=1743498014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/7f0f55288f13f10363bf22985a5d1756.webm?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3422580/extras/7f0f55288f13f10363bf22985a5d1756.mp4?t=1743498014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 unhinged heroes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 reality-bending weapons (Meet your new friend: <i>The Forest Bomber</i>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150+ uncensored item combos (Stack 8 fire speed buffs? Go nuts!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ unique level templates!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-minute fast-paced runs (Perfect for lunch break carnage)!</p></li></ul>",
